e%20alleged%20that%20China%20has%20taken%20America's%20manufacturing%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20taken%20our%20trade%20secrets.%20Now%20it's%20taking%20control%20of%20critical%20industries%2C%20from%20medicines%20to%20advanced%20technology.%20In%20record%20time%2C%20China%20has%20gone%20from%20an%20economically%20backward%20country%20to%20the%20second%20biggest%20economy%20on%20earth%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20every%20intention%20of%20being%20the%20first.%20And%20the%20Communist%20Party's%20motives%20are%20clear.%20They're%20building%20a%20massive%2C%20cutting-edge%20military%2C%20capable%20of%20threatening%20America%20and%20dominating%20Asia%20and%20beyond%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20two-term%20South%20Carolina%20governor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20respects%2C%20China's%20military%20is%20already%20equal%20to%20the%20US%20armed%20forces.%20In%20other%20areas%2C%20they're%20beating%20us.%20China's%20leaders%20are%20so%20confident%2C%20they're%20sending%20spy%20balloons%20into%20our%20skies%20and%20building%20a%20spy%20base%20just%20off%20our%20shores%20in%20Cuba.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20no%20mistake%3A%20The%20Communist%20Party%20is%20preparing%20for%20war.%20And%20China's%20leaders%20intend%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20economic%20plan%2C%20Haley%20said%20it%20includes%20giving%20real%20relief%20and%20financial%20freedom%20to%20middle-class%20Americans.%20Every%20middle-class%20family%20will%20get%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20tax%20relief%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20knows%20how%20to%20use%20your%20money%20better%20than%20you%2C%20no%20one.%20When%20you%20make%20your%20own%20choices%2C%20you%20make%20our%20economy%20even%20stronger%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20starters%2C%20we'll%20completely%20eliminate%20the%20federal%20gas%20and%20diesel%20tax.%20That%20is%2018%20cents%20per%20gallon%20in%20savings%20on%20gas%20and%2024%20cents%20on%20diesel.%20That%20will%20help%20families%20struggling%20with%20record-high%20gas%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20don't%20need%20a%20federal%20gas%20tax%20to%20fund%20our%20roads.%20We'll%20keep%20building%20our%20roads%20with%20the%20trillions%20Washington%20still%20has%20and%20we'll%20stop%20diverting%20money%20to%20green%20giveaways.%20Road%20money%20should%20build%20roads%2C%20not%20bike%20paths%20and%20hiking%20trails%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Ms%20Haley%20said%2C%20she%20would%20also%20cut%20income%20taxes%20for%20working%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20administration%20would%20also%20eliminate%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20USD%20500%20billion%20in%20green%20energy%20subsidies.%20%26quot%3BNo%20more%20cash%20windfalls%20for%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20US%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%20said%20she%20would%20veto%20any%20spending%20bill%20that%20doesn't%20take%20the%20US%20back%20to%20pre-Covid%20spending%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20talking%20about%201950s%20spending%20levels%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20just%20four%20years%20ago.%20We%20had%20a%20massive%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20many%20ways%20a%20foolish%20%E2%80%93%20explosion%20in%20spending%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20But%20the%20pandemic%20is%20over.%20It's%20absurd%20to%20keep%20spending%20at%20those%20same%20crazy%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20my%20plan%2C%20we%20won't%20just%20have%20term%20limits%20for%20politicians%2C%20we%20will%20limit%20bureaucrats%20too.%20No%20bureaucrat%20should%20hold%20the%20same%20position%20for%20more%20than%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20make%20them%20better%20public%20servants%20and%20avoid%20the%20politics%20and%20power%20fiefdoms%20that%20corrupt%20our%20government.%20And%20we%20should%20be%20able%20to%20fire%20those%20who%20are%20not%20performing.%20Public%20service%20is%20a%20privilege%2C%20not%20a%20right.%20And%20no%20one%20has%20a%20right%20to%20roll%20back%20your%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Haley%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695438240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2F49jnjfjc_nikki-haley-reuters_625x300_02_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbeijing-prepping-for-war-china-now-an-existential-threat-for-us-nikki-haley-4416000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Describing%20China%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bexistential%20threat%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20US%20and%20the%20world%2C%20Indian-American%20Republican%20presidential%20aspirant%20Nikki%20Haley%20has%20claimed%20Beijing%20is%20%26quot%3Bpreparing%20for%20war%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbeijing-prepping-for-war-china-now-an-existential-threat-for-us-nikki-haley-4416000%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbeijing-prepping-for-war-china-now-an-existential-threat-for-us-nikki-haley-4416000%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbeijing-prepping-for-war-china-now-an-existential-threat-for-us-nikki-haley-4416000%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTo%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20India%20have%20to%20beat%20.....%26quot%3B%3A%20Gambhir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695438178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103879456%2Cimgsize-102890.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%