osition%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-India%20Star%20Counters%20Gambhir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20fast%20bowler%20S%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sreesanth%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F741-sreesanth-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESreesanth%3C%2Fa%3E%20believes%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20sacrifice%20his%20batting%20position%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20team%20and%20it%20was%20a%20decision%20taken%20consciously%20by%20the%20former%20skipper%20in%20order%20to%20completely%20utilise%20his%20talents%20as%20a%20finisher.%20Sreesanth's%20comments%20came%20in%20connection%20to%20claims%20made%20by%20former%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20said%20that%20Dhoni%20would%20have%20scored%20more%20runs%20if%20he%20batted%20at%20No.%203.%20The%20former%20pacer%20added%20that%20Dhoni%20was%20well%20aware%20about%20the%20positions%20that%20suited%20all%20the%20batters%20and%20it%20was%20his%20finishing%20ability%20that%20helped%20India%20in%20winning%20two%20World%20Cup%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGautam%20Bhai%20said%20recently%20that%20Dhoni%20would%20have%20scored%20more%20runs%20had%20he%20batted%20at%20No.3.%20But%20for%20Dhoni%20it%20was%20always%20about%20more%20victories%20than%20more%20runs.%20He%20always%20had%20the%20ability%20to%20finish%20games%20when%20the%20team%20needed%20him%20and%20he%20won%20two%20World%20Cups%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreesanth%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3D90WJ2XhFVk4%26embeds_referring_euri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sportskeeda.com%252F%26source_ve_path%3DMjg2NjY%26feature%3Demb_logo%5C%2