been%20India's%20No%203%2C%20and%20I%20think%20he%20could%20have%20scored%20more%20than%20what%20he%20has%20scored%20and%20could%20have%20scored%20more%20hundreds%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695431880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F700kp0p_ms-dhoni-innings-_625x300_07_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fms-dhoni-didnt-sacrifice-his-batting-position-ex-india-star-counters-gautam-gambhirs-claim-4414042%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20India%20cricketer%20did%20not%20agree%20with%20Gautam%20Gambhir's%20claims%20that%20MS%20Dhoni%20sacrificed%20his%20batting%20position%20for%20the%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fms-dhoni-didnt-sacrifice-his-batting-position-ex-india-star-counters-gautam-gambhirs-claim-4414042%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fms-dhoni-didnt-sacrifice-his-batting-position-ex-india-star-counters-gautam-gambhirs-claim-4414042%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fms-dhoni-didnt-sacrifice-his-batting-position-ex-india-star-counters-gautam-gambhirs-claim-4414042%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20is%20my%20country%20too%3A%20Rapper%20Shubh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695430845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103878111%2Cimgsize-66352.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-is-my-country-too-rapper-shubh%2Farticleshow%2F103878111.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Punjabi-Canadian%20rapper%20Shubhneet%20Singh%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Shubh%2C%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20over%20the%20cancellation%20of%20his%20India%20tour%20due%20to%20a%20controversial%20social%20media%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ANI%22%2C%22engagem