to%20see%20more%20computing%20power%20available%20to%20biologists.%20So%20I%20was%20very%20excited%20to%20see%20this%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20Anne%20Carpenter%2C%20who%20uses%20computing%20to%20develop%20pharmaceuticals%20at%20the%20Broad%20Institute%20of%20Harvard%20and%20MIT%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20though%20this%20seems%20promising%2C%20the%20project%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E'They're%20not%20announcing%20like%2C%20'We%20have%20created%20a%20model%20that%20does%20a%20particular%20thing.'%20Instead%2C%20they're%20saying%20'We%20are%20planning%20to%20create%20a%20resource%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20available%20for%20biologists%20to%20create%20new%20models%2C'%26quot%3B%20Carpenter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-priscilla-chan-demanded-czi-changes-then-did-two-layoffs-2023-8%5C%22%3EChan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20couple's%20LLC%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theregister.com%2F2023%2F09%2F20%2Fchan_zuckerberg_initiative_to_spin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Register%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20plan%20to%20have%20their%20product%20running%20by%202024.%20The%20company%20also%20declined%20to%20tell%20The%20Register%20how%20much%20it'll%20have%20to%20spend%20to%20make%20its%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20a%20hefty%20bill%2C%20considering%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-triple-production-h100-chips-ai-drives-demand-2023-8%5C%22%3Ecomputer%20parts%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20wants%20to%20use%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20and%20low%20supply%2C%20The%20Register%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20it%20could%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20make%20a%20computer%20system%20made%20of%201%2C000%20graphics%20processing%20units%20%E2%80%94%20electronic%20circuits%20designed%20for%20image%20processing.%20These%20GPUs%20can%20visually%20analyze%20both%20healthy%20and%20diseased%20cells%20from%20databases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20company%20said%2C%20it%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20tool%20available%20to%20the%20public%20so%20that%20researchers%20could%20use%20it%20collaboratively%20to%20make%20new%20discoveries.%20This%20is%20why%20Carpenter%20is%20excited%20about%20their%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20labs%20across%20the%20US%20don't%20have%20equal%20access%20to%20computing%20power%20for%20their%20biotechnology%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20she%20said%2C%20if%20this%20proposal%20is%20accurate%2C%20it%20would%20help%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20researchers%20who%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20look%20for%20new%20therapeutics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22848%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20press%20announcement%20of%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Priscilla%20Chan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650b0d69bf943d00195c6cf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22636%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Priscilla%20Chan%20announced%20their%20initiative%20on%20various%20social%20media%20sites%2C%20including%20Threads%20and%20X.%3Cp%3EChan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20AI%20is%20revolutionizing%20healthcare%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20CZI%20was%20founded%20in%202015%2C%20it%20has%20mainly%20funded%20local%20San%20Francisco%20community%20and%20education%20projects.%20But%20Zuckerberg's%20other%20companies%20have%20forayed%20into%20the%20biotech%20territory%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20produced%20an%20AI%20tool%20in%202022%20called%C2%A0ESMFold%2C%20which%20was%20created%20with%20similar%20AI%20processing%20techniques%20that%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Chan%20say%20could%20be%20used%20on%20their%20new%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EESMFold%20is%20essentially%20a%20faster%20version%20of%20the%2