%20OBC%20Quota%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11162020%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-4.19.30-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20said%20that%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9C100%25%20regret%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20party%20about%20not%20including%20Other%20Backward%20Castes%20(OBC)%20in%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20bill%20passed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-date-set-for-implementation-as-womens-reservation-bill-is-passed-unanimously-by-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%20unanimously%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%2C%20September%2021%2C%20though%20no%20specific%20date%20has%20yet%20been%20set%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhistoric-day-says-pm-modi-as-he-announces-womens-reservation-bill-in-new-parliament%5C%22%3Eimplementation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20the%20legislation%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20works%20for%2027%20years%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-womens-reservation-bill-amit-shah-implementation-2029%5C%22%3Epassed%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20100%25%20regret%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20include%20OBCs%20in%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20that%20was%20passed%20when%20we%20were%20in%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gandhi%20while%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20All%20India%20Congress%20Committee%20(AICC)%20headquarters%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%2022%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20opposition%20parties%20pledged%20their%20support%20to%20the%20Bill%20in%20parliament%2C%20they%20raised%20the%20demand%20for%20sub-quotas%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste%20during%20the%20debate%20in%20both%20Houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20legislation%20states%20that%20one-third%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20by%20amending%20Article%20239AA%2C%20one-third%20of%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20amending%20Article%20330%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20and%20one-third%20seats%20reserved%20in%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20by%20amending%20Article%20332.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22085539%2FF6kk7dvXIAAUkKk.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22085539%2FF6kk7dvXIAAUkKk.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22085539%2FF6kk7dvXIAAUkKk-300x132.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22085539%2FF6kk7dvXIAAUkKk-1024x450.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674214%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22527%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWomen%20MPs%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20after%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne-third%20of%20the%20seats%20currently%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Schedule%20Tribes%20will%20also%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20from%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20opening%20the%20debate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20former%20Congress%20president%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-womens-reservation-debate-congress-renewed-energy%5C%22%3ESonia%20Gandhi%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20raised%20the%20pitch%20for%20sub-quotas%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste%20as%20well%20as%20the%20inclusion%20of%20OBC%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20other%20Congress%20MPs%20including%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20among%20others%20also%20made%20similar%20pitches%20during%20their%20speeches%20in%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20had%20in%202010%20passed%20a%20legislation%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20make%20it%20into%20a%20law.%20The%20Bill%20was%20not%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20Lower%20House%20and%20later%20lapsed%20with%20the%20end%20of%20the%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20Bill%20also%20did%20not%20include%20OBC%20women%2C%20or%20sub-quotas%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste%2C%20as%20the%20Congress%20is%20demanding%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20party%20has%20not%20shifted%20its%20stance%20on%20caste-based%20reservations%20since%20the%202010%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20shifted%20our%20stance%3B%20we%20are%20the%20party%20that%20conducted%20the%20caste%20census.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20release%20the%20data%20of%20the%20caste%20census%3B%20we%20did%20an%20internal%20discussion.%20There%20is%20no%20change%20in%20our%20stance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Bill%20that%20was%20passed%20in%20parliament%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Gandhi%20questioned%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Bill%20is%20great%2C%20a%20critical%20step%20for%20empowerment%20of%20women.%20But%20when%20we%20read%20the%20fine%20print%2C%20we%20found%20two%20footnotes%20stating%20that%20Census%20and%20delimitation%20will%20have%20to%20be%20done%20before%20implementation%20of%20the%20bill.%20It%20will%20take%2010%20years%2C%20or%20maybe%20even%20more%2C%20to%20get%20this%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomen-reservation-implementation-article-81-82-census-delimitation%5C%22%3EWhy%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20May%20Not%20Be%20Implemented%20Even%20in%202029%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20legislation%2C%20while%20providing%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%2C%20however%2C%20adds%20that%20this%20will%20be%20implemented%20only%20after%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20next%20population%20census%20and%20the%20subsequent%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20should%20remove%20the%20two%20clauses%20on%20census%20and%20delimitation%20and%20should%20give%20women%20their%20due%20participation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20should%20also%20release%20the%20data%20from%20the%20last%20caste%20census%20done%20by%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20and%20should%20now%20conduct%20a%20new%20Caste%20census.%20Why%20is%20the%20Modi%20government%20delaying%20the%20process%20of%20conducting%20the%20census%3F%20It%20should%20get%20the%20caste%20census%20done%20now.%20Without%20it%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20power%20to%20the%20deprived%20sections%20of%20our%20country.%20If%20we%20aim%20to%20distribute%20power%20more%20equitably%20in%20India%2C%20we%20need%20data%20on%20caste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20change%20of%20heart%20on%20caste%20census%2C%20says%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20renewed%20its%20pitch%20for%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20at%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20new%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20under%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-calls-for-increasing-upper-limit-on-reservations-at-historic-cwc-meeting%5C%22%3Epledged%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20increase%20the%20upper%20limit%20on%20reservations%20for%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20and%20OBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22221447%2FF6NP0gUXcAAwMNJ.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22221447%2FF6NP0gUXcAAwMNJ.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22221447%2FF6NP0gUXcAAwMNJ-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22221447%2FF6NP0gUXcAAwMNJ-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674440%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20Working%20Committee%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20September%2017%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40INCIndia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%20It%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3Eurged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20implement%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20press%20conference%20on%20Friday%2C%20Gandhi%20also%20promised%20to%20conduct%20the%20caste%20census%20if%20voted%20to%20power%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-calls-for-increasing-upper-limit-on-reservations-at-historic-cwc-meeting%5C%22%3ECongress%20Calls%20for%20Increasing%20Upper%20Limit%20on%20Reservations%20at%20%E2%80%98Historic%E2%80%99%20CWC%20Meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20get%20the%20caste%20census%20done%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20form%20the%20government.%20The%20country%20will%20get%20to%20know%20what%20is%20the%20percentage%20of%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20tribals.%20They%20will%20get%20participation%20in%20running%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20small%20process%3B%20it%20will%20take%20time%20but%20it%20will%20be%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20which%20first%20conducted%20a%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)%20in%202011-12%2C%20but%20never%20released%20its%20data%20because%20of%20varied%20opinions%20about%20it%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%2C%20the%20party%20during%20the%20UPA%20government%20in%202011%20had%20surveyed%20around%2025%20crore%20households%20as%20part%20of%20a%20caste%20census%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20discrepancies%20in%20that%20data%20and%20it%20needed%20cleaning%20up.%20From%202013%20this%20cleanup%20of%20data%20started%20which%20included%20going%20back%20to%20the%20states%20to%20verify%20the%20data%20among%20other%20things.%20The%20cleanup%20of%20the%20data%20was%20done%20by%202014.%20And%20this%20data%20is%20with%20the%20current%20government.%20If%20they%20wanted%20to%20release%20the%20data%20they%20could.%20But%20they%20said%20they%20are%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20release%20the%20data.%20Now%20that%20data%20has%20also%20become%20over%20a%20decade%20old%20so%20can%E2%80%99t%20depend%20on%20that%20data%20so%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20new%20caste%20census%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leader%20said%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20another%20party%20leader%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%2C%20the%20renewed%20pitch%20for%20the%20caste%20census%20from%20the%20party%20does%20not%20reflect%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchange%20of%20heart%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20at%20a%20party%20level%20has%20focused%20on%20different%20issues%20over%20the%20decades%20since%20independence%20depending%20on%20the%20need%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20was%20agriculture%2C%20food%2C%20science%20and%20technology%20or%20globalisation.%20In%20the%20last%20decade%20or%20so%2C%20the%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20party%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20need%20now%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstrengthen%20social%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20policies%20are%20examined%20every%20decade%2C%20and%20in%20the%20past%20ten-odd%20years%2C%20we%20have%20found%20that%20the%20time%20has%20come%20to%20focus%20on%20strengthening%20social%20justice%20and%20bringing%20in%20social%20reforms.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20dynamic%20process%20and%20the%20need%20now%20is%20to%20strengthen%20social%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leader%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20renewed%20pitch%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20moved%20closer%20to%20the%20Mandal-based%20political%20parties%20with%20which%20it%20has%20joined%20hands%20under%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%2C%20which%20have%20been%20clamouring%20for%20the%20caste%20census%E2%80%99s%20implementation%20for%20over%20a%20year%20now.%20Political%20parties%20in%20the%20South%20have%20also%20supported%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20coordination%20meeting%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-to-boycott-tv-shows-that-conduct-inflammatory-debates%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20alliance%20will%20take%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20country%2C%20in%20what%20is%20a%20likely%20hint%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20consensus%20between%20all%20the%20INDIA%20constituents%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695401487000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11162020%2FScreenshot-2023-08-11-at-4.19.30-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F100-regret-in-congress-that-upa-govts-womens-reservation-bill-lacked-obc-quota-rahul-gandhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20in%202010%20passed%20a%20legislation%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20make%20it%20into%20a%20law.%20That%20Bill%20was%20not%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20it%20later%20lapsed%20with%20the%20end%20of%20the%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F100-regret-in-congress-that-upa-govts-womens-reservation-bill-lacked-obc-quota-rahul-gandhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actors%20and%20their%20lavish%20houses%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695401043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103873012%2Cimgsize-92982.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fbollywood-actors-and-their-lavish-houses-in-mumbai%2Fphotostory%2F103873012.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103873012.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBollywood%20actors%20are%20known%20for%20their%20opulent%20lifestyles%20and%20