berculosis%20(DR-TB)%20%E2%80%93%20are%20facing%20an%20acute%20shortage%20of%20the%20necessary%20medicines.%20This%20is%20forcing%20many%20to%20skip%20their%20doses%2C%20a%20choice%20strongly%20discouraged%20in%20any%20tuberculosis%20elimination%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDR-TB%20patients%20are%20those%20for%20whom%20the%20first-line%20of%20TB%20drugs%20have%20not%20worked%20as%20the%20tuberculosis%20bacteria%20in%20them%20has%20become%20resistant.%20So%2C%20they%20are%20prescribed%20a%20more%20advanced%20line%20of%20treatment%20to%20kill%20the%20bacteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajjab%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20a%20driver%20working%20with%20a%20private%20car%20pool%20company%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20wonders%20whether%20the%20UN%20meeting%20would%20lead%20to%20any%20immediate%20solution%20to%20his%20daily%20search%20for%20drugs%20for%20his%20DR-TB%20patient%20wife%2C%20Ruksana.%20She%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20condition%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August%20this%20year.%20She%20was%20prescribed%20three%20drugs%20%E2%80%93%20Cycloserine%2C%20Linezolid%20and%20Clofazimine%20%E2%80%93%20among%20others.%20Ever%20since%20her%20diagnosis%2C%20Khan%20has%20failed%20to%20get%20the%20three%20drugs%20from%20the%20DOTS%20(%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDirectly%20Observed%20Therapy%20Short%20Course%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E)%20centre%20where%20his%20wife%20is%20being%20treated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19133349%2F10146202616_81d4c004a4_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19133349%2F10146202616_81d4c004a4_c.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19133349%2F10146202616_81d4c004a4_c-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Flickr%2FDIVatUSAID%20(CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20is%20a%20driver%20by%20profession%2C%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20daily%20routine%20does%20not%20anymore%20revolve%20around%20ferrying%20riders.%20He%20gets%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20makes%20food%20for%20his%20bed-ridden%20wife%20and%20children%2C%20and%20leaves%20home%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20find%20the%20three%20drugs.%20He%20comes%20back%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20later%20to%20clean%20the%20house%20and%20send%20the%20children%20to%20school.%20Then%20he%20again%20goes%20out%20to%20look%20for%20the%20much-needed%20therapy%20for%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evening%2C%20he%20returns%20empty-handed%2C%20once%20again%2C%20and%20then%20starts%20making%20phone%20calls%20outside%20Mumbai%2C%20or%20even%20Maharashtra%20to%20see%20if%20the%20three%20drugs%20are%20available%20anywhere%20else.%20And%2C%20the%20cycle%20repeats%20day%20after%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20daily%20earnings%20have%20come%20down%20to%20nil%20and%20savings%20have%20exhausted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20wife%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20DR-TB%2C%20we%20were%20warned%20that%20skipping%20a%20meal%20or%20a%20dose%20would%20be%20equivalent%20to%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20neither%20the%20government%20is%20able%20to%20provide%20me%20with%20the%20medicines%2C%20nor%20are%20they%20available%20at%20the%20medical%20stores.%20If%20my%20wife%20dies%2C%20who%20would%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20this%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Khan.%20He%20lives%20in%20the%20slums%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Antop%20Hill%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20others%20such%20as%20Khan%20shared%20a%20similar%20ordeal%20in%20their%20search%20for%20the%20essential%20medicines%20to%20treat%20DR-TB.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20story%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20the%20family%20members%20of%20several%20other%20patients%2C%20the%20people%20and%20communities%20working%20with%20TB%20patients%2C%20and%20the%20concerned%20officials%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20All%20of%20them%20provided%20numerous%20testimonies%20to%20the%20dire%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Ftuberculosis-india-count-who-narendra-modi%5C%22%3EAs%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20TB%20Deadline%20Looms%2C%20Govt%20Must%20Know%20That%20Not%20Counting%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20Option%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20help%20from%20the%20government%20facilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20is%20equally%20%E2%80%9Cconcerned%E2%80%9D.%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20teams%20have%20gone%20to%20at%20least%20four%20states%20in%20India%20to%20assess%20the%20ground%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20assessment%20is%20still%20going%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tereza%20Kasaeva%2C%20director%20of%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Global%20TB%20Programme%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20query%20asked%20at%20a%20virtual%20presser%20held%20a%20day%20before%20the%20UN%20meeting.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20share%20the%20findings%20or%20names%20of%20the%20states%20but%20said%20that%20the%20assessment%20is%20still%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-September%2C%20while%20replying%20to%20an%20email%2C%20which%20was%20sent%20by%20a%20volunteer%20who%20works%20for%20TB%20control%2C%20Kasaeva%20had%20written%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20at%20WHO%20%E2%80%94%20across%20three%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20are%20also%20deeply%20concerned%20and%20closely%20following%20the%20situation%20with%20TB%20drug%20stockout%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20speaking%20about%20%E2%80%9Csystemic%20issues%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20%E2%80%9Cperiodic%20stockouts%E2%80%9D.%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20seen%20a%20copy%20of%20this%20mail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20similar%20tone%2C%20Lucica%20Ditiu%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20%E2%80%98Stop%20TB%20Partnership%E2%80%99%2C%20had%20described%20the%20situation%20as%20%E2%80%9Cworrying%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20said%20that%20her%20programme%20had%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20other%20related%20agencies%20of%20the%20country%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stoptb.org%2F%5C%22%3EStop%20TB%20Partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20entity%20hosted%20by%20the%20UN%20that%20comprises%20multilateral%20agencies%2C%20governments%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20and%20others.%20India%E2%80%99s%20health%20minister%2C%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20is%20currently%20its%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20as%20declared%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20aims%20to%20eliminate%20TB%20by%202025%20%E2%80%93%20five%20years%20prior%20to%20the%20WHO%20goal%20of%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTB%20is%20a%20disease%20that%20is%20very%20unforgiving%20to%20any%20irregularities%20in%20the%20drug%20schedule%20or%20dosing.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20card%20house%20which%20can%20topple%20over%20if%20one%20is%20careless%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Zarir%20F.%20Udwadia%2C%20a%20consultant%20pulmonologist%20with%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Hinduja%20Hospital%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20simple%20words%2C%20missing%20a%20dose%20can%20lead%20to%20worsening%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20as%20the%20bacteria%20would%20become%20resistant%20to%20the%20drugs%20being%20administered.%20It%20can%20even%20lead%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20Khan%2C%20Naushad%20Ali%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20same%20area%2C%20is%20worried%20about%20his%2018-year-old%20daughter%2C%20who%20has%20covered%20a%20major%20part%20of%20her%20treatment%20journey%20for%20DR-TB%20with%20just%20about%20one%20month%20left.%20Naushad%20has%20already%20lost%20his%20wife%20to%20TB%20and%20has%20just%20finished%20the%20treatment%20course%20of%20another%20daughter%20who%20has%20recovered%20from%20the%20deadly%20disease.%20His%20son%20works%20with%20a%20private%20meal%20delivery%20company%20and%20is%20the%20sole%20earning%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20whichever%20area%20of%20Mumbai%20he%20goes%2C%20I%20ask%20him%20to%20enquire%20at%20the%20medical%20stores%20located%20there.%20So%20far%2C%20to%20no%20avail.%20The%20DOTS%20centre%2C%20where%20my%20daughter%20goes%2C%20has%20no%20drugs%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20between%20these%20two%20patients%20is%20that%20while%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20wife%20is%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20the%20treatment%2C%20Naushad%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20is%20in%20the%20last.%20But%20both%20are%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20initial%20or%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintensive%20phase%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20is%20called%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20the%20patient%20has%20to%20become%20non-infective%20(preventing%20transmission%20to%20other%20members)%20and%20test%20negative%20for%20the%20bacteria%2C%E2%80%9D%20explained%20a%20Karnataka-based%20doctor%2C%20who%20has%20an%20experience%20of%20over%20three%20decades%20working%20with%20TB%20patients%20and%20undertaking%20many%20trials.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20a%20member%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20TB%20committees.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20so%20that%20his%20ongoing%20trials%20are%20not%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20slums%2C%20where%20people%20like%20Khan%20and%20Ali%20live%20in%20overcrowded%20spaces%2C%20transmission%20of%20infection%20to%20healthy%20people%20is%20very%20much%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Naushad%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20who%20is%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20her%20treatment%20now%2C%20faces%20a%20risk%20of%20relapse%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20which%20is%20not%20uncommon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Khundi%20village%20of%20Khorda%20district%2C%20Geetanjali%20Pradhan%2C%20whose%20father-in-law%20is%20a%20DR-TB%20patient%2C%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20buy%20the%20drugs%20out%20of%20her%20own%20pocket.%20This%20is%20because%20in%20her%20neighbouring%20village%2C%20a%20TB%20patient%20died%20after%20he%20discontinued%20taking%20medicines%20due%20to%20a%20stock-out%20situation.%20In%20a%20week%2C%20she%20had%20spent%20Rs%204%2C000.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20the%20use%20of%20visiting%20the%20tuberculosis%20unit%20(TU)%20when%20on%20multiple%20visits%20we%20would%20be%20given%20medicines%20only%20for%20three%20days%20or%20a%20week%20%E2%80%93%20that%20too%20on%20an%20irregular%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBijayalaxmi%20Rautaray%20works%20with%20a%20civil%20society%20organisation%2C%20called%20%E2%80%98Sahyog%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20Odisha.%20She%20said%20that%20Cycloserine%20is%20not%20available%20in%20most%20of%20the%20government%20facilities.%20And%20poor%20people%20cannot%20afford%20to%20buy%20it%20from%20the%20private%20market.%20One%20strip%20of%20Cycloserine%2C%20which%20contains%20ten%20tablets%2C%20of%20which%20three%20are%20to%20be%20consumed%20daily%2C%20costs%20Rs%20400.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20Sudeshwar%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20state%20government%20on%20September%208%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20three%20drugs%20were%20not%20available%20at%20the%20government%20facilities%20and%20the%20patients%20were%20forced%20to%20buy%20drugs%20from%20medical%20stores.%20Sudeshwar%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Country%20Coordinating%20Mechanism%20(CCM)%2C%20formed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20tackle%20TB.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20letter%2C%20he%20sent%20a%20collage%20of%20the%20receipts%20of%20purchase%20from%20the%20private%20market.%20The%20receipts%20ranged%20from%20Rs%20300%20to%20Rs%204%2C094.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20September%2020%20that%20his%20situation%20had%20not%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194505%2Fimage-1336.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194505%2Fimage-1336.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194505%2Fimage-1336-300x168.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194505%2Fimage-1336-1024x572.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674414%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194440%2Fimage-1337.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194440%2Fimage-1337.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194440%2Fimage-1337-300x164.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22194440%2Fimage-1337-1024x558.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674413%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22654%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20being%20a%20member%20of%20the%20CCM%2C%20had%20written%20to%20Union%20health%20secretary%20Sudesh%20Pant%20and%20top%20officials%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20TB%20Elimination%20Programme%20on%20September%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20essential%20DR-TB%20medicines%20are%20continuously%20out%20of%20stock%20across%20the%20country%20for%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20as%20confirmed%20by%20the%20digital%20platform%20%E2%80%9CNikshay%20Aushadhi%E2%80%9D%E2%80%A6Sadly%2C%20some%20PWTB%20%5Bpeople%20living%20with%20TB%5D%20are%20forced%20to%20buy%20these%20medicines%20from%20private%20medical%20stores%2C%20causing%20severe%20economic%20hardships%2C%20loss%20of%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20malnutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20letter%20said.%20The%20letter%20he%20sent%20was%20not%20replied%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20explained%20that%20the%20intermittent%20shortages%20started%20from%20last%20year%2C%20but%20since%20June%20the%20situation%20has%20deteriorated.%20He%20was%20not%20the%20only%20person%20who%20had%20written%20to%20the%20government.%20Mumbai-based%20Ganesh%20Acharaya%2C%20a%20TB%20survivor%2C%20who%20also%20works%20with%20TB%20networks%2C%20had%20written%20to%20Union%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20on%20August%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20June%202023%2C%20there%20have%20been%20regular%20reports%20of%20stockouts%20of%20drugs%20used%20to%20treat%20TB%20and%20MDR-%20TB%20in%20several%20DOTS%20%26amp%3B%20DOTS-Plus%20Centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20persistent%20shortages%20have%20affected%20both%20first-%20and%20second-line%20TB%20drugs%2C%20including%20paediatric%20formulations.%20A%20list%20of%20drugs%20that%20have%20been%20out%20of%20stock%20for%20the%20last%20two%20months%20is%20depicted%20herein%20in%20tabular%20form%3A%20Moxifloxacin(Lfx)%2C%20Cycloserine(Cs)%2C%20Linezolid%2C%C2%A0%20Clofazamine%20Pyridoxine%2C%20Delamanid%20FGD-1st%20line%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20letter%20read.%20It%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20financial%20burden%20on%20people%20and%20its%20spillover%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20was%20endorsed%20by%20several%20civil%20society%20groups.%20He%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20even%20his%20letter%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20replied%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fthreat-new-strains-tuberculosis%5C%22%3EThe%20Threat%20of%20New%20Strains%20of%20Tuberculosis%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20lack%20of%20mechanism%20for%20medicine%20procurement%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20several%20reports%20from%20patients%2C%20state%20officials%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20asked%20the%20state%20governments%20to%20procure%20drugs%20on%20their%20own%20from%20April%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBihar%20State%20TB%20control%20officer%20B.K.%20Mishra%20said%20the%20directive%20came%20%E2%80%9Calmost%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20procured%20TB%20drugs%20before%20because%20we%20never%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20it%20%5Bas%20the%20Union%20government%20used%20to%20supply%20it%20earlier%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20placed%20an%20order%20with%20the%20company%20concerned%20for%20Cycloserine.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20supply%E2%80%A6we%20are%20regularly%20following%20up%20with%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMishra%20also%20said%20that%20the%20districts%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20purchase%20the%20drugs%20from%20the%20local%20medical%20stores%20but%20that%20is%20also%20fraught%20with%20uncertainties.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20sure%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20drugs%20available%20with%20the%20medical%20stores.%20And%20now%2C%20if%20we%20enter%20into%20the%20domain%20of%20prequalification%20%5Btesting%20before%20supply%5D%2C%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20further%20delay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20state%20TB%20officer%20from%20one%20of%20the%20states%20listed%20above%20described%20the%20situation%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfrustrating%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20hands%20are%20tied%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20medicines%20I%20can%20purchase.%20If%20I%20have%20to%20go%20beyond%20that%20limit%2C%20the%20file%20has%20to%20move%20several%20desks%2C%20which%20obviously%20means%20further%20delay%20in%20procurement%20and%20supply%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20officer%20added.%20The%20officer%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named%20as%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTelling%20states%20that%20you%20have%20to%20buy%20and%20washing%20your%20hands%20off%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20solution%20because%20there%20is%20no%20mechanism%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Blessina%20Kumar%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Fglobal-coalition-of-tb-advocates%2F%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Coalition%20of%20TB%20Activists%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20an%20international%20platform%20for%20TB%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20tell%20the%20states%20from%20where%20the%20money%20will%20come%20from%2C%20from%20whom%20to%20buy%2C%20how%20the%20prequalification%20of%20drugs%20is%20to%20be%20done%2C%20etc.%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGanesh%20Acharya%2C%20a%20TB%20survivor%2C%20quoted%20above%2C%20also%20pointed%20out%20in%20his%20letter%20that%20there%20are%20potential%20flaws%20and%20problems%20in%20the%20state%20procurement%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDecentralised%20procurement%20of%20this%20kind%20is%20especially%20challenging%20for%20states%20with%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20TB-affected%20people%2C%20limiting%20their%20power%20to%20negotiate%20on%20quantity%2C%20price%2C%20and%20delivery%20timelines%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Ftb-patients-incompatible-with-life-struggle-with-government-policy-on-nutrition%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Incompatible%20With%20Life%E2%80%99%2C%20TB%20Patients%20Struggle%20With%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Policy%20on%20Nutrition%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20worrying%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHad%20the%20decentralisation%20properly%20kicked%20off%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20make%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20TB%20officer%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Khageshwar%20Kumar.%20He%20is%20based%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Koderma%20district.%20He%20is%20a%20treasurer%20of%20the%20TB%20Elimination%20Jharkhand%20Network.%20His%20inquiry%20with%20his%20field%20staff%20and%20concerned%20district%20TB%20officers%20revealed%20that%20Cycloserine%20had%20run%20out%20of%20stock%20in%20at%20least%20two%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20Koderma%20and%20East%20Singhbhum.%20For%20Sahebganj%20district%2C%20the%20drugs%20were%20borrowed%20from%20Dumka%20district%2C%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20September%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Balrampur%20district%2C%20the%20officials%20on%20September%2020%20were%20holding%20a%20meeting%20and%20asking%20the%20health%20officers%20down%20to%20the%20level%20of%20panchayat%20to%20accelerate%20the%20process%20of%20local%20procurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESehjad%20Ahmad%2C%20a%20member%20of%20a%20civil%20society%20group%2C%20who%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20local%20officials%20are%20facing%20issues%20about%20allocating%20budget%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20which%20portion%20of%20the%20budget%20should%20be%20used%20for%20the%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20society%20groups%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20have%20created%20a%20google%20sheet%20to%20update%20the%20stock-out%20position.%20Till%20September%2020%2C%20at%20least%20four%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20Balrampur%2C%20Sravasti%2C%20Siddharthnagar%20and%20Chitrakoot%20%E2%80%93%20reported%20that%20they%20had%20no%20drugs%20available%2C%20according%20to%20Ahmad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20doctors%20are%20deeply%20worried.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20back%20to%20the%20pre-2008%20scenario%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Karnataka-based%20doctor%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9Cas%20it%20was%20an%20era%20when%20people%20in%20India%20hardly%20thought%20about%20drug-resistant%20TB%20patients.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20may%20be%20dying%2C%20or%20have%20already%20died.%20Somebody%2C%20somewhere%2C%20in%20the%20%5Bgovernment%5D%20system%2C%20has%20really%20messed%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20sent%20a%20set%20of%20questions%20to%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%2C%20including%20one%20that%20asked%20for%20a%20timeline%20regarding%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20expectations%20for%20when%20the%20situation%20would%20improve.%20The%20ministry%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20the%20questions%20till%20the%20time%20of%20going%20to%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20responding%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20query%20at%20the%20September%2021%20presser%2C%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Kasaeva%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%2C%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20government%20and%20partners%2C%20that%20this%20unfortunate%20situation%20will%20be%20sorted%20out%20quite%20soon%2C%20as%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20promised%2C%20and%20hopefully%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month%2C%20beginning%20of%20the%20next.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoctors%20and%20individuals%20within%20TB%20communities%20are%20concerned%20about%20whether%20the%20tenders%20have%20been%20placed.%20They%20anticipate%20a%20significant%20time%20lag%20before%20the%20drugs%20reach%20health%20facilities%20and%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPatients%20have%20already%20experienced%20drug%20shortages.%20Even%20if%20the%20buying%20process%20has%20started%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20till%20mid-October%20or%20perhaps%20even%20later%20that%20the%20supply%20becomes%20normal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Blessina.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatients%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20completely%20clueless.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDesh%3C%2Fem%3E%20TB-%3Cem%3Emukt%20nahi%20hoga%2C%20aadmi%20mukt%20ho%20jayega%202025%20se%20pehle%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BTB%20will%20not%20be%20eliminated%20before%202025%20from%20this%20country%20but%20patients%20will%20be%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20a%20patient%20to%20this%20correspondent%20on%20September%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20this%20is%20the%20second%20high-level%20UN%20meeting%20on%20TB.%20The%20first%20one%20was%20held%20in%202018.%20India%E2%80%99s%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20attending%20the%20meet%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695397558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F13090926%2F25372378539_a8d4c4de68_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20Wire'%20spoke%20to%20several%20individuals%20across%20India%2C%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20the%20acute%20shortage%20of%20TB%20drugs%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20WHO%20has%20described%20this%20situation%20as%20'worrying'%2C%20while%20the%20state%20TB%20officials%20call%20it%20'frustrating'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farhan%20%26amp%3B%20SRK%20had%20creative%20differences%20over%20Don%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695397427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103872269%2Cimgsize-36014.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%