there%20is%20any%20element%20of%20terror%20funding%20involved%20from%20across%20the%20border%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fsc-notice-to-tn-govt-udhayanidhi-stalin-on-his-sanatana-dharma-remarks%2Farticle67333837.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20conference%20was%20held%20specifically%20to%20target%20Hinduism%20(also%20referred%20to%20as%20Sanatana%20Dharma)%20and%20to%20abuse%2C%20humiliate%2C%20speak%20in%20derogatory%20language%20and%20spread%20hatred%20towards%20Sanatana%20Dharma%E2%80%A6%20These%20acts%20were%20first%20seen%20in%20Stalinist%20Russia%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20gulags%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petitioner%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20also%20asked%20to%20instruct%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20on%20why%20permission%20was%20given%20for%20such%20a%20conference%20and%20why%20no%20action%20was%20initiated%20against%20the%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%202%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%2C%20at%20the%20conference%2C%20said%20Santana%20Dharma%20is%20like%20dengue%20and%20malaria%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20eradicated%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20huge%20backlash%20from%20Hindutva%20groups%20and%20also%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leaders%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20He%20has%20also%20received%20death%20threats%20following%20the%20comments.%20Notably%2C%20Ayodhya%20seer%20Paramhans%20Acharya%20announced%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20for%20anyone%20who%20beheads%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUndeterred%20by%20the%20reaction%2C%20Udayanidhi%20sharpened%20his%20attack%20on%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20At%20an%20event%20in%20Madurai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20September%2021%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-this-sanatana-dharma-udayanidhi-on-president-murmus-absence-at-new-parliament-inauguration%5C%22%3Esought%20to%20know%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20it%20was%20prescribed%20by%20Santana%20Dharma%20to%20not%20invite%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20a%20widow%20and%20tribal%2C%20for%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20new%20parliament%20building%20was%20inaugurated.%20They%20(Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party)%20got%20the%20Adheenams%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%20the%20inauguration%2C%20but%20the%20President%20of%20India%20was%20not%20invited%20because%20she%20is%20a%20widow%20and%20is%20from%20a%20tribal%20community.%20Is%20this%20Sanatan%20Dharma%3F%E2%80%9D%20Udayanidhi%20had%20asked%20pointedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20President%20Murmu%20was%20not%20invited%2C%20Udayanidhi%20said%20some%20%E2%80%9CHindi%20actors%E2%80%9D%20were%20invited%20to%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20referring%20to%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20and%20Esha%20Gupta%20who%20visited%20the%20parliament%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2020%20%E2%80%93%20the%20day%20when%20the%20first%20session%20was%20held%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695389402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04213611%2FUdhayanidhi.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsantana-dharma-remarks-sc-issues-notice-to-tamil-nadu-government-udayanidhi-stalin%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20petition%20was%20moved%20before%20the%20apex%20court%20seeking%20a%20CBI%20probe%20against%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20and%20organisers%20of%20the%20conference%20where%20the%20remarks%20were%20made.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsantana-dharma-remarks-sc-issues-notice-to-tamil-nadu-government-udayanidhi-stalin%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20GI-Tagged%20Mithais%20You%20Must%20Try%20%26amp%3B%20The%20Amazing%20Stories%20Behind%20Them%22%2