armoured%20vehicles%2C%20planes%2C%20and%20ammunition%20that%20were%20key%20to%20preventing%20Russia%20from%20attacking%20Ukraine%20and%20potentially%20other%20EU%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Poland%2C%E2%80%9D%20M%C3%BCller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWarsaw%20has%20supplied%20Ukraine%20with%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20weaponry%2C%20including%20Leopard%202%20tanks%20and%20Soviet-era%20MiG%20fighter%20jets%20for%20use%20in%20the%20war%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20months%20of%20the%20war%2C%20when%20other%20EU%20countries%20talked%20about%20support%2C%20Poland%20consistently%20helped%20repel%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20%E2%80%98misinterpreted%E2%80%99%20on%20Ukraine%20arms%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuda%20doubled%20down%20on%20Thursday%2C%20arguing%20Morawiecki%E2%80%99s%20threat%20to%20stop%20providing%20weapons%20to%20Kyiv%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinterpreted%20in%20the%20worst%20way%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20meant%20that%20%5BPoland%5D%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20transferring%20to%20Ukraine%20the%20new%20weaponry%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20currently%20buying%20as%20we%20modernise%20the%20Polish%20army%2C%E2%80%9D%20Duda%20told%20TVN24%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWarsaw%20has%20signed%20multiple%20arms%20deals%20recently%2C%20including%20with%20the%20US%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20from%20whom%20it%20ordered%20K2%20%E2%80%9CBlack%20Panther%E2%80%9D%20tanks%20and%20K9%20howitzers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20receive%20the%20new%20weaponry%20from%20the%20US%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20we%20will%20be%20releasing%20the%20weaponry%20currently%20used%20by%20the%20Polish%20army.%20Perhaps%20we%20will%20transfer%20it%20to%20Ukraine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Duda%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarta%20Prochwicz-Jazowska%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20the%20Warsaw%20office%20of%20the%20German%20Marshall%2