the%20future.%20For%20once%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20the%20present%20and%20find%20what%20I%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Vivek%20(44)%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDesiring%20a%20respite%20from%20the%20demands%20of%20life%20and%20yearning%20to%20%E2%80%9Csit%20on%20a%20mountain%2C%20read%20books%2C%20and%20disconnect%20from%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Major%20Vivek%20Jacob%20contemplated%20early%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20given%20my%20country%20and%20my%20work%20all%20that%20I%20could.%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20for%20me%20to%20move%20on%20to%20a%20different%20facet%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20However%2C%20as%20unpredictable%20as%20life%20can%20be%2C%20this%20choice%20took%20the%20major%20down%20a%20path%20he%20may%20have%20never%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20he%20runs%20an%20organisation%20called%20CLAW%20Global%20(Conquer%20Land%2C%20Air%2C%20Water)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20impact%20venture%20working%20towards%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306209%2Fbengaluru-ngo-gives-horticulture-training-to-people-with-disability-provides-job-placements%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20people%20with%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20way%20of%20sports.%20Major%20Jacob%20not%20only%20trains%20them%20but%20also%20leads%20them%20on%20exhilarating%20adventures%2C%20such%20as%20scuba%20diving%2C%20sky%20diving%2C%20and%20mountaineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20prompted%20this%20profound%20shift%20from%20seeking%20respite%20to%20founding%20an%20organisation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20military%20service%20to%20empowering%20the%20disabled%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20part%20of%209%20Para%20Special%20Forces%2C%20in%202015%2C%20Major%20Vivek%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20while%20training%20and%20injured%20his%20spine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20he%20met%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20Bhaduria%20who%20was%20paralysed%20waist%20down%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20due%20to%20an%20accident.%20The%20lieutenant%20had%20dived%20into%20a%20pool%20and%20hit%20his%20head%2C%20injuring%20his%20neck%20which%20left%20him%20paralysed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20time%20in%20the%20military%20hospital%2C%20as%20I%20recovered%2C%20I%20closely%20observed%20how%20hard%20my%20friend%E2%80%99s%20life%20was.%20He%20was%20suffering%20and%20losing%20hope%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCTsIGnpIHeu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCTsIGnpIHeu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCTsIGnpIHeu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20C.L.A.W%20%E2%80%93%20Conquer%20Land%20Air%20Water%20(%40claw_global)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EA%20swimming%20enthusiast%2C%20the%20lieutenant%20would%20often%20ask%20the%20Major%2C%20%E2%80%9CWill%20I%20ever%20scuba%20dive%20again%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20time%20on%20my%20hands%20and%20I%20started%20to%20research%20and%20found%20what%20people%20have%20done%20despite%20disabilities.%20I%20showed%20those%20videos%20to%20him%20and%20all%20he%20could%20say%20was%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20this%20is%20possible%20for%20me%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sight%20of%20his%20dejected%20friend%20was%20unbearable%20to%20the%20Major.%20So%20he%20promised%20the%20lieutenant%20that%20he%20would%20make%20it%20happen%20for%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20made%20a%20resolution%20in%20my%20heart%20to%20help%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20became%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20the%20Major%E2%80%99s%20life%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20work%20in%20this%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20he%20voluntarily%20took%20an%20early%20retirement%20with%20a%20purpose%20in%20hand.%20The%20organisation%20CLAW%20Global%20was%20founded%20in%202019%20and%20has%20trained%20200%20people%20with%20disabilities%20in%20different%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282597%2Fwoman-escapes-abusive-marriage-starts-adventure-sports-company-green-trek-assam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20adventure%20sports.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCLAW%20Global%20is%20not%20just%20an%20organisation%20that%20trains%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20it%20also%20tries%20to%20reinstill%20hope%20among%20them.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20positive%20energy%20they%20had%20and%20wanted%20to%20harness%20it%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Finding%20ability%20in%20disabilities%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20with%20a%20core%20team%20of%20six%20members%20along%20with%2010%20other%20members%2C%20the%20organisation%20trains%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20paralysis%2C%20terminal%20diseases%2C%20visual%20impairments%2C%20and%20amputees%20%E2%80%94%20in%20adventure%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20the%20time%20when%20he%20started%20brainstorming%20the%20idea%2C%20the%20Major%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20my%20research%2C%20I%20had%20one%20and%20only%20one%20goal%20in%20mind%20%E2%80%94%20take%20my%20friend%20scuba%20diving.%20So%20naturally%2C%20I%20started%20looking%20into%20the%20kind%20of%20resources%20required%20for%20a%20person%20with%20a%20disability%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CLAW%20Global%20has%20trained%20over%20200%20people%20in%20different%20types%20of%20adventure%20sports.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330672%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECLAW%20Global%20has%20trained%20over%20200%20people%20in%20different%20types%20of%20adventure%20sports.%