3E.%20The%20Bard%20was%20obviously%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20names%20are%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20these%20fresh%20openings%2C%20the%20BJP-Modi%20combine%20was%20handed%20another%20playing%20card%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhat-is-sanatana-dharma%5C%22%3ESanatan%20Dharma%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Misquoting%20or%20distorting%20words%20of%20the%20tallest%20of%20nationalist%20icons%20%E2%80%93%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%2C%20even%20while%20glossing%20over%20arguments%20of%20their%20icons%20%E2%80%93%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20and%20M.S.%20Golwalkar%20%E2%80%93%20is%20unsurprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Sanatanis%2C%20despite%20their%20numerical%20strength%2C%20are%20not%20the%20only%20Hindus%2C%20and%20even%20people%20believing%20in%20the%20so-called%20Indic%20(do%20not%20ask%20if%20this%20word%20does%20not%20have%20similarities%20with%20India)%20religions%20do%20not%20owe%20allegiance%20to%20this%20sect.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20showcasing%20all%20Hindus%20as%20Sanatanis%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20as%20anti-Hindu.%20Is%20this%20not%20a%20familiar%20ploy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20much%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20various%20Indian%2FBharatiya%20rivers%20since%20January.%20There%20are%20multiple%20causes%20behind%20Modi%20encountering%20an%20awkward%20terrain%20and%20calls%20for%20a%20different%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20recognise%20the%20resulting%20anxiety%20that%20has%20pushed%20Modi%20to%20recklessly%20strap%20up%20issues%20with%20the%20forbidding%20potential%20of%20acting%20as%20flashpoints%20and%20reopening%20fissures%20on%20lines%20of%20religion%2C%20region%2C%20and%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20worries%20may%20eventually%20be%20transitory%20or%20even%20illusory%2C%20and%20Modi%20could%20well%20overcome%20the%20challenge%20and%20assuredly%20head%20into%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%