%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-soumya-ranjan-patnaik-expelled-media-baron%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20Uptick%20in%20Violence%20Ahead%20of%20Winter%2C%20Possibility%20of%20Fresh%20Infiltration%20Along%20the%20LoC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F04170315%2F15693039226_bc366e1bf3_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ahead%20of%20the%20winter%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20witnessing%20a%20spike%20in%20violence%20against%20security%20forces%20who%20have%20faced%20high%20incidence%20of%20casualties%20this%20year%20despite%20a%20remarkable%20decline%20in%20militancy-related%20incidents%2C%20official%20and%20public%20data%20reviewed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%2030%20security%20personnel%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20151%20incidents%20of%20militancy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202022%2C%20the%20toll%20of%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20union%20territory%20has%20reached%2022%20in%20just%2052%20incidents%20till%20September%2022%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20South%20Asia%20Terrorism%20Portal%20(SATP)%2C%20which%20monitors%20violence%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%20official%20data%20shows%20that%20eight%20security%20personnel%20were%20killed%20in%20Kashmir%20which%20includes%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%5C%22%3E%20two%20Army%20officers%20and%20a%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20four%20personnel%20who%20were%20gunned%20down%20in%20a%20single%20incident%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%20region%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFour%20civilians%2C%20including%20a%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%2C%20were%20also%20killed%20in%20terror%20incidents%20in%20the%20valley%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20Additional%20Director