0which%20separates%20Jammu%20division%20from%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20and%20even%20reportedly%20crossing%20back%20the%20LoC%20into%20Pakistan%20occupied%20J%26amp%3BK%20(PoJ%26amp%3BK)%20after%20carrying%20out%20deadly%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20and%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20shows%20that%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20army%20soldiers%20and%20dozens%20of%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20militant%20attacks%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%20in%20Pir%20Panjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwho-is-uzair-bashir-khan-the-kashmiri-militant-behind-the-deadly-kokernag-attack%5C%22%3EWho%20Was%20Uzair%20Bashir%20Khan%2C%20the%20Kashmiri%20Militant%20Behind%20the%20Deadly%20Kokernag%20Attack%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20fortnight%20alone%2C%20security%20forces%20and%20militants%20were%20caught%20in%20at%20least%20six%20face-offs%20across%20the%20union%20territory%2C%20including%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20the%20capital%2C%20where%20an%20unidentified%20militant%20opened%20fire%20on%20a%20truck%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Paramilitary%20Forces%20(CRPF)%20in%20Khanyar%20locality%20on%20September%2018%20but%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20cause%20any%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFour%20of%20these%20face-offs%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20or%20its%20adjoining%20areas.%20Some%20of%20these%20face-offs%20have%20turned%20deadly%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20six%20security%20personnel%2C%20including%20three%20officers%2C%20in%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20anti-militancy%20operation%20in%20Kokernag.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20seven%20militants%20were%20also%20gunned%20down%20over%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20of%20which%20six%20militants%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EInfiltration%20woes%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20activity%20of%20militants%20in%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%20has%20prompted%20officials%20to%20relook%20at%20the%20winter%20strategy%20for%20containing%20militancy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Officials%20and%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2F5-incidents-in-10-days-cross-border-spike-turns-gaze-to-winter-strategy-8943188%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20increasing%20violence%20points%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20fresh%20infiltration%20along%20the%20LoC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20uptick%20in%20violence%20is%20consistent%20with%20the%20past%20trends%20as%20foreign%20militants%20try%20to%20sneak%20across%20the%20LoC%20before%20the%20winter%20snow%20on%20high%20mountain%20passes%20makes%20J%26amp%3BK%20inaccessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20two%20years%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20has%20accused%20Islamabad%20of%20violating%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fafter-february-ceasefire-agreement-first-pakistani-sporting-team-arrives-in-india%5C%22%3E2011%20Ceasefire%20Agreement%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20vowed%20to%20uphold%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20by%20providing%20%E2%80%9Cfire%20support%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20group%20of%20infiltrators%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20were%20later%20gunned%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20insurgency-related%20violence%20has%20quieted%2C%20the%20number%20of%20active%20militants%20breached%20the%20double-digit%20mark%20achieved%20last%20year%20to%20reach%20107%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20including%2071%20foreign%20militants.%20This%20has%20raised%20red-flags%20in%20the%20security%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20national%20English%20daily%20reported%20that%20only%2081%20militants%20were%20active%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20the%20month%20of%20August.%20The%20report%20excludes%20the%20number%20of%20%E2%80%98hybrid%E2%80%99%20militants%2C%20a%20new%20term%20used%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20to%20describe%20the%20militants%20who%20have%20not%20been%20identified%20due%20to%20their%20undercover%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUptick%20in%20militancy%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20and%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20there%20are%2015%20active%20militants%20in%20Jammu%20region%20with%20two%20of%20them%20believed%20to%20be%20foreigners.%20But%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20militants%20are%20shifting%20bases%20between%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20indicates%20that%20the%20number%20could%20be%20on%20the%20higher%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2070%25%20militants%20active%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20affiliated%20with%20Pakistan-based%20Jaish-e-Mohammad%20and%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20outfits%20which%2C%20officials%20believe%2C%20operate%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Peoples%20Anti-Fascist%20Force%20and%20The%20Resistance%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20over%20600%20overground%20workers%20of%20militants%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20anti-terror%20laws%20with%20most%20of%20them%20incarcerated%20in%20jails%20outside%20the%20union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20significant%20development%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Jammu%20police%20was%20sent%20on%20a%20central%20deputation%20earlier%20this%20week%20while%20the%20head%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Paramilitary%20Forces%E2%80%99%20Kashmir%20operations%20was%20prematurely%20repatriated%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMukesh%20Singh%2C%20a%201996%20IPS%20officer%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20Jammu%2C%20(ADGP)%20since%202019%2C%20has%20been%20sent%20on%20a%20central%20deputation%20with%20the%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20(ITBP)%20for%20five%20years%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695378296000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%