20family%20members%20have%20been%20made.%20The%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20previous%20statement%2C%20the%20Winnipeg%20police%20said%20that%20on%20September%2020%2C%20at%20around%2010%20am%2C%20the%20North%20District%20General%20Patrol%20Officers%2C%20assisted%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Tactical%20Support%20Team%2C%20went%20to%20a%20residence%20in%20the%20200%20block%20of%20Hazelton%20Drive%2C%20where%20they%20located%20the%20deceased%20adult%20victim.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGill%E2%80%99s%20killing%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20ongoing%20standoff%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20and%20claims%20by%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20that%20India%20was%20behind%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Sukha%20Duneke%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESukhdool%20Singh%20Gill%20alias%20Sukha%20Duneke%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20Duneke%20village%20of%20Moga%20district.%20Sukha%E2%80%99s%20name%20had%20figured%20in%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%E2%80%99s%20wanted%20list%2C%20which%20was%20released%20on%20September%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGill%20allegedly%20reached%20Canada%20on%20a%20fake%20passport%20in%202017.%20Before%20fleeing%20to%20Canada%2C%20he%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20peon%20in%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20Moga.%20He%20had%20got%20this%20job%20on%20compassionate%20grounds%20after%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGill%20was%20allegedly%20associated%20with%20the%20Bambiha%20gang%20led%20by%20gangster%20Davinder%20Bambiha%20notorious%20for%20gang%20wars%2C%20extortion%20and%20killings%20in%20parts%20of%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20over%2016%20cases%20registered%20against%20him%20in%20different%20police%20stations.%20His%20name%20had%20also%20figured%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20renowned%20international%20kabaddi%20player%20Sandeep%20Singh%20from%20Jalandhar%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20SSP%20Moga%20J.%20Elanchezhian%20confirmed%20Gill%E2%80%99s%20killing%20and%20said%20that%20he%20was%20facing%20over%2015%2F16%20cases%20of%20extortion%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%20murder%20cases.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20close%20to%20pro-Khalistani%20gangster%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20Dalla.%20We%20also%20contacted%20Sukha%E2%80%99s%20paternal%20uncle%2C%20who%20shared%20that%20his%20sister%20called%20up%20from%20Canada%20and%20informed%20them%20about%20his%20killing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGills%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20militancy%20in%20Punjab.%20His%20father%20Naib%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20a%20diesel%20tanker%20driver%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20militants%20in%201989%20in%20Kotkapura%20situated%20in%20Faridkot%20district%20while%20he%20was%20returning%20home.%20Later%2C%20Gill%20got%20a%20job%20in%20the%20Moga%20deputy%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20on%20compassionate%20grounds%2C%20but%20he%20quit%20within%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20landing%20in%20Canada%2C%20Gill%20along%20with%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20Dalla%20alias%20Arsh%20Dalla%2C%20who%20too%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20Dalla%20village%20in%20Moga%20district%2C%20allegedly%20led%20a%20network%20of%20gangsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDalla%20was%20declared%20a%20%E2%80%98listed%20terrorist%E2%80%99%20under%20the%20UAPA%20in%20January%20this%20year.%20He%20was%20accused%20of%20various%20offences%2C%20including%20targeted%20killings%2C%20attempted%20murder%20and%20extortion%20for%20raising%20funds%20for%20terrorist%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695376556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21112117%2FF6hdCSnWEAAyAr2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanad