ng%20network.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20something%20we%20take%20seriously.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20we%20will%20keep%20working%20on%2C%20and%20we%20will%20do%20that%20regardless%20of%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20not%20some%20special%20exemption%20you%20get%20for%20actions%20like%20this.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20country%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20up%20and%20defend%20our%20basic%20principles.%C2%A0%20And%20we%20will%20also%20consult%20closely%20with%20allies%20like%20Canada%20as%20they%20pursue%20their%20law%20enforcement%20and%20diplomatic%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sullivan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20probably%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-trudeau-india-murder-us-uk-australia%5C%22%3Estrongest%20statement%20from%20the%20United%20States%20backing%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3Estood%20up%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20on%20Monday%2C%20September%2018%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20had%20claimed%20that%20authorities%20were%20pursuing%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%20of%20a%20potential%20link%20between%20agents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%E2%80%9D.%20India%20had%20termed%20the%20allegations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%20and%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%20After%20Canada%20expelled%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20India%20also%20did%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20explosive%20statement%2C%20there%20had%20been%20focus%20on%20the%20reaction%20of%20the%20other%20Five%20Eyes%20states%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20been%20closely%20working%20with%20India%20to%20prop%20it%20up%20as%20a%20counter-weight%20to%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAustralia%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20had%20said%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-trudeau-india-murder-us-uk-australia%5C%22%3Edeeply%20concerned%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20allegations.%20The%20Australian%20foreign%20minister%20Penny%20Wong%20said%20that%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20had%20been%20conveyed%20to%20India.%20Both%20Australia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20asked%20India%20to%20join%20the%20Canadian%20investigation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20an%20article%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Canada%20had%20pushed%20its%20alliance%20partners%20to%20issue%20a%20joint%20statement%20to%20condemn%20India%20for%20violating%20international%20law.%20It%20claimed%20that%20several%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20rebuffed%20Canada%20on%20this%20proposal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20article%20was%20widely%20circulated%20in%20the%20Indian%20and%20Canadian%20media%20with%20commentary%20that%20the%20United%20States%20had%20been%20muted%20in%20its%20support%20for%20Ottawa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20official%20rebuttal%2C%20not%20surprisingly%2C%20came%20from%20the%20Canadian%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20which%20denied%20that%20Ottawa%20had%20broached%20such%20a%20proposal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20public%20broadcaster%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fcanada-india-nijjar-sikh-trudeau-modi-1.6971670%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20an%20anonymous%20senior%20US%20administration%20official%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20strenuously%20denying%20the%20%3Cem%3EWaPo%3C%2Fem%3E%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20US%20national%20security%20council%20spokesperson%20Adrienne%20Watson%20tweeting%20that%20the%20article%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNSC_Spox%2Fstatus%2F1704516397554884715%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eflatly%20false%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20Washington%20supported%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20law%20enforcement%20efforts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20answers%20at%20the%20White%20House%20briefing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20NSA%20Sullivan%20also%20attempted%20to%20reinforce%20the%20line%20that%20US%20had%20been%20at%20the%20front%20in%20supporting%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20soon%20as%20we%20heard%20from%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20publicly%20about%20the%20allegations%2C%20we%20went%20out%20publicly%20ourselves%20and%20expressed%20our%20deep%20concern%20about%20them%2C%20our%20support%20for%20a%20law%20enforcement%20process%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20exactly%20what%20happened%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20held%20accountable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESullivan%20also%20referred%20to%20having%20seen%20attempts%20in%20the%20media%20%E2%80%9Cto%20try%20to%20drive%20a%20wedge%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Canada%20on%20this%20issue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20firmly%20reject%20the%20idea%20that%20there%20is%20a%20wedge%20between%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Canada.%C2%A0%20We%20have%20deep%20concerns%20about%20the%20allegations%2C%20and%20we%20would%20like%20to%20see%20this%20investigation%20carried%20forward%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20held%20to%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20a%20query%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20US%20had%20got%20evidence%20to%20support%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20claim%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20answer%20directly.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20going%20to%20speak%20to%20either%20intelligence%20or%20law%20enforcement%20matters%20from%20this%20podium.%20I%20will%20let%20that%20process%20play%20out.%20We%20are%20in%2C%20as%20I%20said%20before%2C%20continuous%20communication%20and%20consultation%20with%20the%20Canadian%20government.%20And%20we%20will%20remain%20so%20as%20we%20go%20forward%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fsikh-nijjar-india-canada-trudeau-modi-1.6974607%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECanada%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20quoted%20Canadian%20government%20sources%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20saying%20that%20it%20had%20obtained%20human%20and%20signals%20intelligence%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20an%20unnamed%20Five%20Eye%20member%20had%20also%20provided%20some%20evidence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Sullivan%20strongly%20supported%20Canada%2C%20he%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20directly%20criticise%20India.%20Sullivan%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20answer%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20President%20Biden%20to%20speak%20with%20the%20Indian%20PM%20on%20this%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20going%20to%20get%20into%20private%20diplomatic%20conversations%20that%20have%20either%20already%20happened%20or%20are%20going%20to%20happen%20on%20this%20topic%2C%20only%20to%20say%20that%20we%20have%20been%20and%20will%20be%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20Indians%20at%20high%20levels%20on%20this%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F54721d57-fe1b-4d28-ab9b-a664f110770b%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%