usly-by-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%20Session%E2%80%9D%20(not%20waiting%20for%20the%20scheduled%20Winter%20Session)%20of%20parliament%2C%20as%20if%20to%20have%20the%20measure%20implemented%20in%20the%20coming%20assembly%20elections%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20course%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20another%20decorative%20candle%20to%20be%20dangled%20with%20yet%20another%20golden%20promise%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20some%20future%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20the%20Bill%20stipulates%20that%20the%20reservation%20will%20be%20implemented%20only%20after%20a%20national%20census%20is%20held%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20nationwide%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20delimitation%20exercise%20may%20of%20course%20prove%20to%20be%20the%20most%20contentious%20political%20battleground%20than%20anything%20we%20have%20seen%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20way%20may%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20be%20rearranged%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2Fgerrymandering%5C%22%3Egerrymandered%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20you%20know%20what%20I%20mean)%20in%20order%20to%20produce%20the%20maximum%20fruit%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20we%20do%20not%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwith-delimitation-now-complete-jk-politicians-allege-further-disempowerment-of-kashmir%5C%22%3Ediscredited%20delimitation%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20anything%20to%20go%20by%2C%20that%20nationwide%20exercise%20may%20take%20forever%2C%20and%20then%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsider%20that%20the%20southern%20states%2C%20having%20performed%20far%20better%20in%20matters%20of%20development%20and%20population%20control%2C%20will%20stand%20to%20lose%20to%20those%20other%20states%20whose%20numbers%20have%20swelled%20with%20no%20comparable%20growth%20to%20boast%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20for%20fair%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWill%20then%20the%20expansion%20of%20constituencies%20in%20northern%20states%20and%20their%20shrinkage%20in%20the%20south%20receive%20happy%20agreement%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThink%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Bill%20thus%20has%20clearly%20been%20a%20proposal%20with%20no%20date%20for%20a%20happy%20nuptial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsider%20that%20had%20the%20Modi%20government%20indeed%20wanted%20grandly%20to%20implement%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20the%20assemblies%2C%20it%20would%20have%20brought%20on%20the%20Bill%20at%20the%20inception%20of%20its%20takeover%20of%20state%20power%2C%20giving%20itself%20room%20to%20accomplish%20the%20historic%20deed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAny%20good%20reason%20why%20this%20was%20not%20done%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20most%20men%20folk%20who%20aspire%20to%20parliament%20may%20make%20progressive%20noises%20but%20are%20at%20heart%20distressed%20by%20the%20prospect%20of%20losing%20their%20perches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20matter%20of%20content%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20and%20indeed%20most%20parties%20who%20constitute%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20of%20opposition%20parties%2C%20have%20now%20thrown%20a%20political%20spanner%20into%20the%20ruling%20juggernaut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20about%20the%20inclusion%20of%20women%20who%20belong%20to%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20dreadful%20catch-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20especially%20Shri%20Modi%2C%20has%20been%20courting%20this%20class%20of%20Indians%2C%20how%20may%20they%20explain%20the%20exclusion%20of%20their%20women%20members%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Bill%2C%20since%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20are%20included%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20anomaly%20set%20to%20unleash%20another%20Mandal%20movement%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20yes%2C%20this%20may%20indeed%20prove%20too%20hot%20for%20the%20saffronites%20to%20manipulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20if%20they%20do%20concede%20the%20demand%2C%20how%20may%20they%20refuse%20OBC%20menfolk%20the%20same%20benefit%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20cult%20then%20succeed%20in%20persuading%20India%E2%80%99s%20women%20that%20its%20intentions%20have%20been%20clean%2C%20or%20will%20most%20citizens%20see%20through%20the%20subterfuge%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20the%20fifteen%20lakh%20for%20each%20citizen%20did%20not%20come%2C%20nor%20did%20the%20two%20crore%20jobs%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENor%20did%20the%20income%20of%20our%20farmers%20double%20as%20was%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20these%2C%20as%20the%20now%20honourable%20home%20minister%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Famit-shah-calls-modi-bluff-2111288%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20were%20just%20%3Cem%3Echunavi%20jumlas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(poll%20gimmicks)%2C%20why%20may%20India%E2%80%99s%20very%20smart%20women%20believe%20that%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Bill%20will%20become%20a%20reality%20should%20the%20BJP%20come%20back%20to%20power%20in%202024%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fat%20is%20in%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20no%20telling%20what%20cuisine%20may%20or%20may%20not%20come%20forth%20to%20the%20feminine%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBadri%20Raina%20taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695371362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22125932%2FH20230922139320.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwomens-reservation-modi-government-hurry-propose-not-wed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20the%20Modi%20government%20truly%20wanted%20to%20implement%20reservation%20for%20women%2C%20would%20it%20not%20have%20passed%20the%20Bill%20at%20the%20inception%20of%20its%20takeove