dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-1695302803-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330509%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESadhya%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20traditionally%20served%20on%20a%20banana%20leaf%20and%20comprises%20dozens%20of%20dishes%20including%20rice%2C%20curries%2C%20and%20desserts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ETypically%20at%20their%20restaurant%2C%20Margaret%20and%20Vinod%20offer%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%2015%20items%20including%20%3Cem%3Ematta%20rice%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20has%20a%20nutty%20flavour%3B%20%3Cem%3Esambar%3C%2Fem%3E%20prepared%20with%20okra%2C%20carrots%2C%20and%20potatoes%2C%20%3Cem%3Eavial%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20is%20considered%20the%20%E2%80%98queen%20of%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mildly-spiced%20vegetable%20dish%20cooked%20in%20a%20thick%20coconut%20and%20yogurt%20mixture%3B%20%3Cem%3Ekaalan%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20elephant%20yam%20cooked%20in%20yogurt%20and%20flavored%20with%20fenugreek%20%E2%80%93%20that%20adds%20a%20tangy%20note%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20this%2C%20they%20also%20serve%20ginger%20and%20tamarind%20condiments%2C%20%3Cem%3Epappadam%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20lentil%20wafers%20to%20be%20crushed%20on%20rice%20and%20curries.%20As%20no%20Onam%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20complete%20without%20%3Cem%3Epayasam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20dish%20is%20prominently%20featured%20on%20their%20menu%20too.%20The%20lip-smacking%20food%20is%20finished%20off%20with%20a%20generous%20dash%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20childhood%20memories%20of%20relishing%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Vinod%20(54)%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20that%20the%20entire%20family%20would%20come%20together%20to%20prepare%20the%20Onam%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20it