health%20in%20many%20instances%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20family%20always%20came%20to%20her%20rescue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeing%20chased%20by%20rhinos%20to%20climbing%20trees%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20the%20field%20director%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%20she%20has%20held%20several%20other%20titles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest%20Officer)%20at%20Kokrajhar%20where%20I%20managed%20a%20sanctuary%20and%20a%20highly%20endemic%20primate%20species%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Golden%20Langur%20or%20%3Cem%3ESonali%20Bandor.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%20My%20namesake%20and%20I%20have%20since%20then%20shared%20a%20special%20bond%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20lovingly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20of%20her%20favourite%20workplaces%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20fortunate%20to%20have%20served%20at%20Manas%20National%20Park%20with%20its%20sheer%20natural%20beauty%20and%20unique%20conservation%20and%20governance%20models.%20It%20taught%20me%20that%20there%20are%20many%20sides%20to%20a%20coin%20and%20one%20must%20appreciate%20history%20to%20become%20an%20effective%20administrator.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESonali%20also%20served%20a%20tenure%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Zoo%20in%20Delhi%20before%20she%20accepted%20the%20role%20at%20Kaziranga.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20Kaziranga%20her%20%3Cem%3EKarma%20Bhoomi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(land%20of%20action)%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshe%20fondly%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20career%20in%20the%20state%20at%20Kaziranga%20as%20a%20probationary%20trainee.%20At%20that%20time%20I%20was%2020%20years%20younger%20and%2020%20kg%20lighter!%20So%20when%20a%20rhino%20chased%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20courage%20and%20strength%20to%20climb%20a%20tree!%20I%20dread%20what%20will%20happen%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20a%20range%20of%20vital%20tasks%2C%20from%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%2C%20to%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20She%20also%20engages%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20delving%20into%20their%20reliance%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20exploring%20avenues%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215138%2Fsustainable-e-commerce-karnival-shopping-online-eco-friendly-homegrown-products-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Ghosh's%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-4-1695301285-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGhosh%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20responsibilities%20encompass%20patrolling%20and%20surveillance%20to%20thwart%20poachers%20and%20coming%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20wild%20animals%20in%20distress.%20Picture%20Credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20role%20demands%20precise%20monitoring%20of%20wildlife%20through%20scientific%20techniques%20and%20the%20careful%20management%20of%20tourism%20through%20the%20creation%20and%20execution%20of%20ecotourism%20initiatives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20her%20work%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20need%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20listener%20and%20understand%20how%20this%20famed%20protected%20area%20works.%20I%20have%20a%20great%20team%20with%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20forest%20frontline-to-area%20ratios%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20priority%20would%20be%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20protection%2C%20ensure%20and%20strengthen%20Rhinoceros%20and%20other%20flagship%20species%E2%80%99%20conservation.%20The%20second%20priority%20would%20be%20the%20utmost%20welfare%20of%20the%20forest%20frontline%20staff%20who%20serve%2024%C3%977%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20conditions%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20has%20only%20been%2020%20days%20since%20Sonali%20assumed%20the%20new%20responsibility%2C%20she%20is%20quite%20geared%20up%20for%20the%20upcoming%20workload.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20great%20responsibility%20and%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20giving%20me%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20wait%20to%20give%20my%20best%20to%20nature%20and%20conserve%20the%20wildlife%20of%20the%20national%20park%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20women%20aspiring%20to%20be%20in%20the%20field%20of%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservation%20in%20India%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20and%20young%20ladies%20who%20love%20outdoors%20and%20want%20to%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20mus