mising%20they%20would%20not%20get%20me%20married%20till%20I%20turned%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jyotsana%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20a%20student%20in%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20the%20initiative%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20battle%20against%20child%20marriages%20in%20Tripura%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBeti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20started%20in%202020%20by%20the%20then%20collector%20Debapriya%20Bardhan%20to%20educate%20girls%20on%20adolescence%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20But%20the%20initiative%20turned%20dormant%20as%20schools%20shut%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257746%2Fias-hero-karnataka-ceo-zilla-parishad-prevents-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Saju%20Vaheed%20%E2%80%94%20a%202015%20batch%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Kerala%20%E2%80%94%20took%20over%20and%20joined%20as%20the%20Collector%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20and%20revived%20the%20initiative%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Saju%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20reviving%20this%20project%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20many%20female%20students%20of%20Classes%208%2C%209%2C%20and%2010%20were%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%20The%20education%20department%20informed%20me%20that%20it%20was%20because%20of%20child%20marriages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20IAS%20officer%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20in%20mid-2022%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20survey%20and%20found%20out%20that%20215%20such%20girls%20got%20married%20in%202020%20and%20the%20number%20was%20209%20in%202021.%20This%20comprised%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20dropout%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20they%20observed%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20when%20they%20were%20between%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20that%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20were%20entering%20puberty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA