ww.thebetterindia.com%2F258900%2Fcoronavirus-origin-professor-padmanabhan-balaram-dorothy-hamre-unsung-woman-scientist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esevere%20pneumonia%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20fever%20and%20cough%20for%20three%20days%20along%20with%20a%20low%20platelet%20count%20and%20died%20of%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20in%20the%20emergency%20room.%20Although%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hail%20from%20the%20same%20village%20as%20the%20index%20case%2C%20the%20doctors%20were%20alert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20would%20a%20healthy%2C%20young%20adult%20die%20of%20pneumonia%20in%20just%20three%20days%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20unusual%20in%20the%20case%20of%20normal%20bronchopneumonia.%20We%20started%20probing%20in%20detail.%20We%20followed%20the%20Nipah%20protocols%20in%20handling%20the%20body%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20it%20to%20the%20family.%C2%A0We%20sent%20his%20sample%20also%20to%20NIV%20the%20same%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20there%20was%20an%20overlap%20between%20this%20patient%20and%20the%20first%20patient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20relative%20who%20was%20being%20treated%20in%20the%20same%20hospital%20as%20the%20index%20case.%20We%20got%20the%20discharge%20summary%20of%20that%20patient%20to%20establish%20the%20exact%20connection.%20He%20had%20been%20in%20the%20same%20ICU%20as%20the%20first%20patient%20who%20died%20on%2029%20August%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20critical%20care%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2042-year-old%20man%20and%20two%20of%20the%20four%20admitted%20tested%20positive%20for%20Nipah%20virus.%20Three%20others%20have%20also%20tested%20positive%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20Nipah%20cases%20currently%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20helped%20the%20state%20government%20establish%20containment%20zones%20and%20trace%20all%20contacts%20of%20these%20patients%20and%20isolate%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%202018%20experience%20helped%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kerala%20government%20has%20increased%20surveillance%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330119%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKerala%20government%20has%20increased%20testing%20and%20created%20containment%20zones%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20enabled%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20quick%20thinking%20was%20his%20experience%20in%202018.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20at%20Baby%20Memorial%20Hospital%2C%20Kozhikode%2C%20who%20had%20identified%20the%20first%20cases%20of%20the%20virus%20in%20the%20state%20in%20May%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%20recalls%2C%20three%20members%20of%20a%20family%20were%20admitted%20with%20fever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20patient%20had%20severe%20encephalitis%20(inflammation%20of%20the%20brain).%20On%20evaluation%2C%20we%20found%20that%20his%20brother%20had%20died%20two%20weeks%20back%20with%20unusual%20symptoms.%20So%20the%20same%20three%20conditions%2C%20clustering%20of%20cases%2C%20unusual%20clinical%20symptoms%2C%20and%20contact%20with%20an%20index%20case%20gave%20us%20suspicion%20of%20a%20rare%20virus.%20Some%20symptoms%20mimicked%20Nipah%20and%20we%20sent%20the%20sample%20to%20Manipal%20virology%20institute%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20patients%20also%20lived%20near%20Janaki%20forest%2C%20home%20to%20many%20bat%20species.%20Fruit%20bats%20in%20a%20forest%20area%20here%20had%20tested%20positive%20for%20Nipah%20in%202018.%20Coincidentally%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%20hails%20from%20Ulliyeri%20village%2C%20which%20is%20just%2020%20kms%20from%20Janaki%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nipah%20outbreaks%20in%202018%2C%202019%20and%202021%20all%20presented%20with%20encephalitis%20symptoms.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20the%20symptoms%20are%20flu-like%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20diagnosis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20symptoms%20mimic%20flu%2C%20along%20with%20some%20central%20nervous%20system%20symptoms%20like%20confusion%2C%20convulsions%2C%20seizures.%20This%20time%20the%20presentation%20is%20very%20different.%20This%20is%20the%20season%20when%20influenza%20and%20pneumonia%20cases%20are%20a%20lot.%20We%20have%20to%20look%20carefully%20at%20family%20history%20and%20blood%20work.%20Most%20of%20these%20patients%20have%20low%20platelet%20count%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kumar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doctor%20was%20part%20of%20the%20medical%20teams%20in%202018%20and%202023%20who%20first%20diagnosed%20the%20virus%2C%20and%20helped%20in%20even%20faster%20discovery%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20in%202018%2C%20it%20took%2036%20hours%20for%20diagnosis%2C%20while%20this%20time%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20diagnose%20in%20just%2012%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20should%20you%20watch%20out%20for%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww