1-2-1694786653-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-2-1694786653-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20has%20several%20windows%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%20and%20keep%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Anupa%20Kurian%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20have%20taken%20a%20JCB%20just%20minutes%20to%20break%20the%20place%20down%2C%20but%20all%20the%20bricks%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20waste.%20Because%20of%20using%20manual%20labour%20instead%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20use%20those%20bricks%20in%20constructing%20some%20of%20the%20extensions%20in%20my%20room%20and%20the%20patio%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20father%20was%20against%20removing%20the%20garage%20and%20constructing%20a%20patio%2C%20presently%20he%20is%20the%20one%20who%20uses%20it%20the%20most!%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%20where%20Anupa%20chose%20to%20keep%20the%20originality%20of%20the%20house%20is%20with%20the%20roof%20rafters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20was%20built%20using%20wooden%20rafters%20and%20most%20of%20the%20people%20advised%20us%20to%20change%20it%20to%20steel.%20However%2C%20on%20inspection%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20roof%20was%20stronger%20than%20ever.%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20against%20all%20that%20advice%20and%20kept%20the%20original%20rafters%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Today%2C%20the%20wooden%20rafters%20give%20the%20house%20a%20rustic%20and%20more%20traditional%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChampioning%20sustainability%20during%20renovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnuja%20further%20shares%20that%20to%20keep%20the%20house%3